[B]Ok, now I am confuse and angry at Verant to have given us such a bad rule book!

I was told by a GM and confirm by the player's handbook, that DEX only affect missile attacks and spell casting but I always hear Monks saying that having a high DEX make a difference in battle so, what else does it affect?

I've heard that it helps getting max dmg more often and that it helps Dual Wield and Double Attack but it seems to be pure speculation, not true knowledge.

I want facts from experimentation or true knowledge, not opinions. I hope Verant will put a better rule book in the expension!

Thanks[/B][/QUOTE]

